import {
  AppBar,
  Box,
  Button,
  IconButton,
  Toolbar,
  Typography,
} from "@mui/material";

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <AppBar color={primary.light} elevation={0}>
        <Toolbar variant="dense" sx={{ minHeight: "auto", py: "8px" }}>
          <Box mx={4}>
            <IconButton></IconButton>
          </Box>
          <Box mx={3}>
            <Typography sx={{ color: "white", fontWeight: "bold" }}>
              견적비교
            </Typography>
          </Box>
          <Box mx={3}>
            <Typography sx={{ color: "white", fontWeight: "bold" }}>
              핸드캐리
            </Typography>
          </Box>
          <Box mx={3}>
            <Typography sx={{ color: "white", fontWeight: "bold" }}>
              마이페이지
            </Typography>
          </Box>
          <Box sx={{ flexGrow: 1 }}></Box>
          {/* 버튼을 오른쪽으로 배치하기 위한 코드 */}
          <Box>
            <Button
              sx={{
                backgroundColor: "#11ac0a",
                color: "white",
                borderRadius: 5,
                ":hover": { backgroundColor: "#11ac0a" },
                textTransform: "none",
                whiteSpace: "nowrap",
              }}
            >
              Log In / Sign Up{" "}
            </Button>
          </Box>
        </Toolbar>
      </AppBar>
    </>
  );
};

export default Header;
